  "description": "A fairly advanced refrigerator from the popular South Korean brand Samsung, first of all, notable for its good capacity, full support for No Frost technology, inverter compressor and the ability to integrate into a smart home system. The manufacturer equipped the device with ultra-thin highly efficient insulation, which made it possible to expand the capacity of the model with fairly standard overall dimensions of the case. Thus, the total useful volume of the working chambers reaches 344 liters. The capacity of the refrigeration compartment is 230 liters, and the freezer located underneath is 114 liters. The 'smart' refrigerator Samsung Grand + RB34C600DSA, among other things, boasts a double cooling circuit, due to which the working chambers have separate heat exchangers and a separate ventilation system. Also, due to this, it becomes possible to fine-tune the temperature in the refrigerator and freezer chambers. Additionally, mixing of odors between the compartments is prevented. The back side of the refrigerator, where the condenser is located, is completely covered with a protective cover, thanks to which the product can be moved close to the walls, as well as mounted in kitchen furniture. The inverter power unit Digital Inverter is used for the compressor. This is a digital inverter with 7 performance stages.",
